---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';
---

<Layout title="Managed AI for Ecommerce | AG-Website" description="We engineer and run your managed AI commerce operations, replacing manual roles with autonomous systems.">
	<Header />
	
	<main class="container">
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="hero animate-fade-in">
			<div class="badge">Ecommerce Industry</div>
			<h1>
				We Engineer and Run Your <span class="text-gradient">Managed AI Commerce Operations</span>
			</h1>
			
			<div class="hero-pills">
				<div class="body-pill">
					Systemize Operations. <span class="bold">Unlock Durable Growth.</span>
				</div>
				<a href="/contact" class="use-cases-pill">
					Let's Chat <span class="icon-dots">⁛</span>
				</a>
			</div>

			<p class="hero-subtext">
				We build and operate autonomous systems for brands moving too fast for spreadsheets but unwilling to justify slow, expensive enterprise tech bloat. Replacing fragmented tools with a single managed operations layer.
			</p>
		</section>

		<!-- The Problem / Operations Decay Section -->
		<section class="dark-block">
			<div class="block-header">
				<span class="sub-heading">The Scaling Problem</span>
				<h2>Operations Decay and Quietly Break Down</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="problem-grid">
				<div class="problem-card">
					<div class="status-indicator"></div>
					<h3>Headcount Bloat</h3>
					<p>Relying on manual execution means headcount increases without clear ownership or autonomous work.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="problem-card">
					<div class="status-indicator"></div>
					<h3>Execution Slowness</h3>
					<p>Fixes require manual coordination and dependency on specific people, making updates take weeks instead of days.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="problem-card">
					<div class="status-indicator"></div>
					<h3>Data Drift</h3>
					<p>Data standards drift away across Shopify and channels, leading to edge cases and fragmented systems.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Pillars of Service -->
		<section class="feature-section">
			<div class="section-badge">How We Deliver</div>
			<h2>Core Autonomous Infrastructure</h2>
			
			<div class="grid grid-3">
				<div class="nolo-card">
					<div class="card-icon">🏗️</div>
					<h3>Managed Product Catalog</h3>
					<p>Centralized AI-synced hierarchies that scale across your entire catalog, attributes, and variant groups.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="nolo-card">
					<div class="card-icon">📦</div>
					<h3>Autonomous Inventory</h3>
					<p>A replenishment system that balances velocity, seasonality, and thresholds with auto-triggered POs.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="nolo-card">
					<div class="card-icon">🚛</div>
					<h3>Logistics Intelligence</h3>
					<p>Proactive monitoring of inbound shipments and exceptions, maintaining ETAs without manual oversight.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="nolo-card">
					<div class="card-icon">🔍</div>
					<h3>Discoverability & SEO</h3>
					<p>Crawlable taxonomies and intents engineered for natural language discovery and agentic commerce systems.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="nolo-card">
					<div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
					<h3>Managed Web Execution</h3>
					<p>Ongoing optimization of collection logic, filters, and site structure directly from structured data.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="nolo-card">
					<div class="card-icon">🧠</div>
					<h3>Operational Support</h3>
					<p>No single point of failure. Proactive fixes and system evolution as your ecommerce business grows.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Impact / Value Prop -->
		<section class="impact-section">
			<div class="impact-content">
				<h2>One Unified System. Zero Fragmented Roles.</h2>
				<p>We replace multiple operational roles with one streamlined autonomous system, bridging the gap from growth to enterprise scale.</p>
				<div class="cta-wrap">
					<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start Building Now</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<style>
		/* Hero Styles (inherited from index but refined) */
		.hero {
			padding: var(--space-xl) 0 4rem;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			text-align: center;
			background-image: radial-gradient(var(--border-muted) 1.2px, transparent 1.2px);
			background-size: 30px 30px;
			background-position: center;
			min-height: 80vh;
			justify-content: center;
		}
		
		h1 {
			font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
			max-width: 1100px;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			font-weight: 800;
			line-height: 0.95;
		}

		.text-gradient {
			color: var(--accent-primary);
		}

		.hero-subtext {
			max-width: 800px;
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			line-height: 1.6;
			color: var(--text-secondary);
			margin-top: 1.5rem;
			font-weight: 500;
		}

		.badge {
			background: var(--bg-dark);
			color: var(--text-on-dark);
			padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
			border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 0.1em;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		/* Pill Styles */
		.hero-pills {
			display: flex;
			gap: 1rem;
			margin: 2rem 0;
			justify-content: center;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}
		.body-pill {
			background: #FFC2CE;
			border: 2px solid #1A1A1A;
			padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
			border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
			color: #1A1A1A;
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			font-weight: 500;
			display: inline-flex;
			align-items: center;
			box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #1A1A1A;
		}
		.body-pill .bold { font-weight: 800; margin-left: 5px; }
		
		.use-cases-pill {
			background: #FFFFFF;
			border: 2px solid #1A1A1A;
			padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
			border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
			color: #1A1A1A;
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			display: inline-flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 0.75rem;
			box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #1A1A1A;
			transition: all 0.2s ease;
		}
		.use-cases-pill:hover { transform: translate(-2px, -2px); box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #1A1A1A; }
		.icon-dots { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; }

		/* Dark Block (Scaling Problems) */
		.dark-block {
			background: #1A1A1A;
			color: #FFFFFF;
			padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md);
			border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
			margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
			border: 2px solid #000;
			box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--accent-primary);
		}
		.block-header {
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: 4rem;
		}
		.block-header h2 {
			color: #FFFFFF;
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			margin-top: 1rem;
		}
		.sub-heading {
			color: var(--accent-primary);
			text-transform: uppercase;
			font-size: 0.85rem;
			font-weight: 800;
			letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		}

		.problem-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
			gap: 3rem;
		}
		.problem-card {
			padding: 2.5rem;
			border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
			border-radius: var(--radius-md);
			background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		}
		.problem-card h3 {
			color: #FFFFFF;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}
		.problem-card p {
			color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
		.status-indicator {
			width: 32px;
			height: 32px;
			background: var(--accent-primary);
			border-radius: 4px;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			display: block;
		}

		/* Features Section */
		.feature-section {
			padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
		}
		.section-badge {
			display: inline-block;
			background: var(--accent-primary);
			color: white;
			padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
			border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			font-weight: 800;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}
		.feature-section h2 {
			font-size: 3rem;
			margin-bottom: 4rem;
		}

		/* Nolo Card styling */
		.nolo-card {
			padding: 3rem;
			background: var(--bg-secondary);
			border: 2px solid #1A1A1A;
			border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
			box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #1A1A1A;
			transition: all 0.2s ease;
		}
		.nolo-card:hover { transform: translate(-2px, -2px); box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 #1A1A1A; }
		.card-icon {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			display: block;
		}
		.nolo-card h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
		.nolo-card p { color: var(--text-secondary); }

		/* Impact Section */
		.impact-section {
			padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
			background: var(--bg-primary);
			border-top: 2px solid #1A1A1A;
			margin-top: 4rem;
			text-align: center;
		}
		.impact-content h2 {
			font-size: 3.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}
		.impact-content p {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			max-width: 700px;
			margin: 0 auto 3rem;
			color: var(--text-secondary);
		}

		.btn {
			padding: 1.25rem 3.5rem;
			border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
			font-weight: 800;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			font-size: 1rem;
			transition: all 0.2s ease;
			display: inline-block;
			border: 3px solid #1A1A1A;
			box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #1A1A1A;
		}
		.btn-primary {
			background: var(--accent-primary);
			color: white;
		}
		.btn-primary:hover {
            background: #1A1A1A;
            color: white;
			transform: translate(-3px, -3px);
			box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--accent-primary);
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
			.hero-pills { flex-direction: column; }
			.impact-content h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
